title: Monoprice iPhone 11 Pro Max (6.5) Rugged Slim Case - Clear -Scratch Resistance, Drop Protection from Up to 6Ft. - Form Collection
features: Premium materials: form slim protective cases are manufactured using genuine, optically-clear Virgin materials from Germany that have been UV-stabilized to resist yellowing over time. The case not only feels good to hold, but looks great as well.

Exceptional fit: all form cases are meticulously designed and engineered to exacting standards to ensure a snug fit around your iPhone while providing easy access to buttons, speakers, microphones, and connectors.

Ultra slim, Ultra protected: featuring three air Cushions per corner that disperse energy upon impact, the slim protective case meets military standard 810G 516.6 for drop protection from up to six feet.

Raised corners and bezels offer added protection for the screen and camera lenses, while a high 5H hardness polycarbonate back resists scratches, keeping your case looking new for a longer period of time.
description: The form slim protective case is a thin, protective, and stylish solution for the day-to-day wear and tear on your iPhone. The case is manufactured using genuine, optically-clear Virgin materials from Germany that have been UV-Stabilized to resist yellowing over time. Its ultra slim yet Ultra protective design meets military standard 810G 516.6 for drop protection from up to six feet.
